<div style="margin: auto; width: 600px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13px; height: 46px; text-align: right; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 50px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(102, 102, 102);">
        <a style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;" href="#" target="_blank">{rc_mallDomain}</a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 50px;">
        <div><font color="#444444" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: -2px;">您的<b>密码</b>已<b>更改</b>成功。</span></font><br><font color="#444444" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: -2px;"><img style="margin-top: -40px; margin-right: 10px; float: right;" alt="password change top image" src="/data/mail/img/mailimg_password-change.png"></span></font>
        </div>
        <div style="line-height: 22px; margin-top: 30px;"><font color="#555555" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 13px;">您好，这里是<b>{rc_mallNm}</b>。</span></font><br><font color="#555555" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 13px;">{rc_memNm}，您有更改密码记录。</span></font><br></div>
    </div>
    <div style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">更改明细</div>
    <table class="__se_tbl_ext" style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13px; width: inherit; border-top: 1px solid rgb(186, 186, 186); border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td style="height: 43px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 229, 229); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);">用户名</td>
            <td style="width: 70%; height: 43px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 229, 229); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;">{rc_memId}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="height: 43px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"><font color="#888888">密码更改日期</font></td><td style="width: 70%; height: 43px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px; border-bottom-color: rgb(229, 229, 229); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;">{rc_changeDt}</td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <div style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13px; padding-top: 20px;">
        <p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px;">- 如果您没有更改密码，请联系客服中心。</p>
        <p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 22px; font-size: 12px;">- 请安全管理密码，不要让其他人知道您的密码。<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;谢谢。</p>
    </div>
    <div style="color: rgb(218, 218, 218); font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 70px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;"></div>
    <div style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 20px;"><!--{ @ gd_get_footer_logo_tag() }-->{=.tag}<!--{ / }--> </div>
    <div style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
        <p>本邮件为发信专用，不能回复。其他咨询，请联系<a href="#" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;">[客服中心]</a>。<br></p>
        <p style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 11px;">Copyright(C) <b style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 11px;">{rc_mallNm}</b> All right reserved.</p>
